#. <section class="sutta" id="sn38.13"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn38.13:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 38"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 38"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn38.13:0.2"
msgid "1. Jambukhādakavagga"
msgstr "1. With Jambukhādaka"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn38.13:0.3"
msgid "13. Bhavapañhāsutta"
msgstr "13. A Question About States of Existence"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi4.259"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn38.13:1.1"
msgid "“‘Bhavo, bhavo’ti, āvuso sāriputta, vuccati."
msgstr ""
"“Reverend Sāriputta, they speak of these things called ‘states of existence’."

msgctxt "sn38.13:1.2"
msgid "Katamo nu kho, āvuso, bhavo”ti?"
msgstr "What are states of existence?”"

msgctxt "sn38.13:1.3"
msgid "“Tayome, āvuso, bhavā."
msgstr "“Reverend, there are these three states of existence."

msgctxt "sn38.13:1.4"
msgid "Kāmabhavo, rūpabhavo, arūpabhavo—"
msgstr ""
"Existence in the sensual realm, the realm of luminous form, and the formless "
"realm."

msgctxt "sn38.13:1.5"
msgid "ime kho, āvuso, tayo bhavā”ti."
msgstr "These are the three states of existence.”"

msgctxt "sn38.13:1.6"
msgid "“Atthi panāvuso, maggo atthi paṭipadā, etesaṃ bhavānaṃ pariññāyā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“But, reverend, is there a path and a practice for completely understanding "
"these three states of existence?”"

msgctxt "sn38.13:1.7"
msgid "“Atthi kho, āvuso, maggo atthi paṭipadā, etesaṃ bhavānaṃ pariññāyā”ti."
msgstr "“There is.” …"

msgctxt "sn38.13:1.8"
msgid "“Katamo, panāvuso, maggo katamā paṭipadā, etesaṃ bhavānaṃ pariññāyā”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn38.13:1.9"
msgid ""
"“Ayameva kho, āvuso, ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo, etesaṃ bhavānaṃ pariññāya, "
"seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn38.13:1.10"
msgid "sammādiṭṭhi … pe … sammāsamādhi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn38.13:1.11"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, āvuso, maggo ayaṃ paṭipadā, etesaṃ bhavānaṃ pariññāyā”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn38.13:1.12"
msgid "“Bhaddako, āvuso, maggo bhaddikā paṭipadā, etesaṃ bhavānaṃ pariññāya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn38.13:1.13"
msgid "Alañca panāvuso sāriputta, appamādāyā”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn38.13:1.14"
msgid "Terasamaṃ."
msgstr ""
